 <p>
  <div list-type="simple" class="list">
   <div id="o0005" class="list-item">
    <span class="label">•</span>
    <p>QM calculations show that Ca
     <span class="sup">2+</span> binds to γGlu47 in connexin hemichannels.
    </p>
   </div>
   <div id="o0010" class="list-item">
    <span class="label">•</span>
    <p>Molecular models of increasing size are employed in hybrid DFT calculations.</p>
   </div>
   <div id="o0015" class="list-item">
    <span class="label">•</span>
    <p>Ca
     <span class="sup">2+</span> binding affects the interaction between γGlu47 and Arg75, Arg184.
    </p>
   </div>
   <div id="o0020" class="list-item">
    <span class="label">•</span>
    <p>Ca
     <span class="sup">2+</span> binding alters the structure in a critical region of connexin hemichannels.
    </p>
   </div>
